Date: Fri, 5 Dec 2025 12:07:48 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 17/40] platform: mellanox: mlx-platform: Add support DGX
 flavor of 400GB/s ethernet switch.
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This system is based on Nvidia SN4700 Spectrum™-3 Based 32x400Gb/s ETH
Switch System, with the
following key changes:

Key changes:
- New Power Supply: AC/DC PSUs power repaced by rack busbar input power
  ORv3 DC 48V-54V.
- Dimensions MGX/DGX 1U compliance Tool-less top cover (fast cover
  opening with no scre

System class: VMOD0010
System SKU: HI184

Reviewed-by: Vadim Pasternak vadimp@mellanox.com

Signed-off-by: Oleksandr Shamray <oleksandrs@nvidia.com>
---
